                Your parcel will be waiting in the system until the goods are arrived at our warehouse in China.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row setup-content step hiddenStepInfo" id="step-6">
        <div class="col-xs-12">
            <div class="col-md-12 well text-center">
